\c 58
\s Ukuzila ukudla okuyikho
\p
\v 1 Memeza\x + 40.3.\x* ngomphimbo, ungayekeli\x + 54.2.\x*, uphakamise ilizwi lakho njengophondo\x + Levi 25.9. Jow. 2.1. 1 Kor. 14.8.\x*, utshele abantu bami isiphambeko sabo, lendlu kaJakobe izono zabo.
\v 2 Kanti bayangidinga mina usuku ngosuku, bethokoza ukwazi indlela zami\x + Jobe 21.14.\x*; njengesizwe esenza ukulunga, esingadelanga isimiso sikaNkulunkulu waso, babuza kimi izimiso zokulunga, bathokoza\x + Mat. 13.20.\x* ekusondeleni kuNkulunkulu.
\p
\v 3 \add Besithi\add*: Kungani sizile ukudla\x + Mal. 3.14.\x*, wena-ke ungaboni\x + 56.12.\x*? \add Kungani\add* sihluphe umphefumulo wethu\x + 58.5. Levi 16.29.\x*, wena-ke ungakwazi? Khangelani, ngosuku lokuzila kwenu ukudla, lithola intokozo, licindezele\x + 60.17.\x* zonke izisebenzi zenu\x + Zaga 5.10.\x*.
\v 4 Khangelani, lizila ukudla\x + 1 Kho. 21.9,12,13.\x* lisenzela ingxabano lokuphikisana, lokutshaya ngenqindi yenkohlakalo; lingazili ukudla njengalamuhla, ukwenza ilizwi lenu lizwakale phezulu\x + Mat. 6.7.\x*.
\v 5 Kunjalo yini ukuzila ukudla engikukhethileyo\x + Zek. 7.5.\x*? Lusuku lokuthi umuntu ahluphe umphefumulo\x + 58.5. Levi 16.29.\x* wakhe yini? Ukuthi akhothamise ikhanda lakhe njengomhlanga\x + 9.14. 19.15.\x*, endlale\x + Esta 4.3. Hlab. 139.8.\x* \add phansi kwakhe\add* isaka lomlotha\x + Jona 3.6. Esta 4.1. Mat. 6.16.\x*? Lokhu ungakubiza yini \add ngokuthi\add* yikuzila ukudla, losuku olwemukelekayo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni?
\v 6 Kayisikho lokhu yini ukuzila ukudla engikukhethileyo: Ukuthukulula izibopho zobubi\x + Hlab. 73.4. Seb. 8.23.\x*, ukukhulula\x + Neh. 5.10-12.\x* imichilo yejogwe, ukuyekela abacindezelweyo bahambe bekhululekile\x + Jer. 34.9. Luka 4.18.\x*, lokuthi lephule lonke ijogwe?
\v 7 Kayisikho yini ukwabela olambileyo isinkwa sakho\x + 58.10. Hez. 18.7,16. Mat. 25.35.\x*\x + Luka 3.11.\x*, lokungenisa abayanga\x + 58.10. Hez. 18.7,16. Mat. 25.35.\x* \add abay\add*imihambuma endlini\x + Hlab. 68.6.\x*, lapho ubona onqunu umembese\x + Luka 3.11.\x*\x + Jobe 31.19.\x*, lokuthi ungacatsheli inyama yakho\x + Neh. 5.5. Gen. 29.14. 1 Tim. 5.8.\x*?
\p
\v 8 Khona ukukhanya kwakho\x + 58.10. Jobe 11.17.\x* kuzaqhamuka njengokusa, lokusila\x + Jer. 8.22. 30.17. 33.6.\x* kwakho kuhlume masinyane; lokulunga kwakho kuhambe phambi kwakho; inkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* ibe ngumvikeli wakho ngasemuva.
\v 9 Khona uzabiza, iN\nd kosi\nd* iphendule, uzakhala, ibisisithi: Khangela ngi\add lapha\add*. Uba ususa phakathi kwakho ijogwe, ukukhomba \add ngo\add*munwe\x + Zaga 6.13.\x*, lokukhuluma okubi\x + Hlab. 12.2.\x*,
\v 10 ukhuphele olambileyo umphefumulo wakho\x + Hlab. 144.13. Zaga 8.35.\x*\x + 58.7.\x*, usuthise umphefumulo ohluphekileyo\x + 58.11.\x*, khona ukukhanya kwakho\x + 58.10. Jobe 11.17.\x* kuzaphuma emnyameni, lobumnyama bakho bube njengemini enkulu.
\v 11 Njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* izakukhokhela njalonjalo\x + Hlab. 48.14.\x*, isuthise umphefumulo wakho\x + 58.11.\x* engwaduleni, iqinise amathambo akho, ube njengesivande esithelelwayo\x + Jer. 31.12.\x*, lanjengomthombo wamanzi, omanzi awo angapheliyo.
\v 12 Labakho bazakwakha\x + 61.4. Neh. 4.6,17-21.\x* amanxiwa amadala\x + 52.9.\x*; uzavusa izisekelo zezizukulwana ngezizukulwana; uzabizwa \add ngokuthi\add*: UMvalisikhala\x + Hez. 22.30.\x*, uMbuyiseli wemikhondo yokuhlala.
\s Ukugcinwa kwesabatha
\p
\v 13 Uba uphendula unyawo lwakho lusuka kusabatha\x + 56.2,4,6. Neh. 10.31. 13.15-22.\x*, u\add ng\add*enz\add i\add* intokozo yakho ngosuku lwami olungcwele; ulibize isabatha \add ngokuthi\add* yintokozo\x + 13.22.\x*, olungcwele lweN\nd kosi\nd*, oluhloniphekayo; njalo uluhlonipha, ungenzi indlela zakho\x + 66.3.\x*, ungatholi intokozo yakho, loba ukhulume ilizwi \add lakho\add*,
\v 14 khona uzazithokozisa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 57.4.\x*, ngizakugadisa\x + Dute. 32.13.\x* ezindaweni eziphakemeyo zomhlaba\x + Dute. 32.13.\x*\x + 2 Sam. 22.34.\x*, ngizakwenza udle ilifa likaJakobe uyihlo; ngoba umlomo weN\nd kosi\nd* ukhulumile\x + 1.20.\x*.
